          %i.fa.fa-mobile.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
        %h4.service-heading Mobile
        %p.text-muted Built for your mobile devices from the ground up. Pinching and zooming is for nerds. Enjoy text you can read, maps you can see, and forms you can enter.

      .col-md-4
        %span.fa-stack.fa-4x
          %i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
          %i.fa.fa-flag-checkered.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
